  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/ac071b7dc4e4b3228fa578ad5ae56474.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2><br>Coin Factory is a relaxing money-making game where you'll embark on a journey to wealth. Combine and level up factories, explore numerous synergies at your own pace, and unlock multiple tiers of buildings. Compete in daily challenge levels with exclusive bonus buildings, adding a special flavor to your experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/a924f6e62fc82ad505066420eda56683.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/a924f6e62fc82ad505066420eda56683.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/a924f6e62fc82ad505066420eda56683.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Community</h2><br>Join us on our Discord to share your strategies and highlights! Our team values your ideas and feedback; we aim for Coin Factory to provide a great relaxing experience for everybody.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Start by planning your strategy and placing your output tile. This tile will receive all the money you make and make it available for you to buy upgrades and new tiles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/cf10a6cb0918446e86ecacab454e9126.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/cf10a6cb0918446e86ecacab454e9126.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/cf10a6cb0918446e86ecacab454e9126.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From here, it's all about building up! Level up your factories and place better modifier factories to enhance your production. Discover the best matches and uncover secrets that will give you an advantage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/75ca8748795e0ee4476e6db9ee89861a.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/75ca8748795e0ee4476e6db9ee89861a.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/75ca8748795e0ee4476e6db9ee89861a.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have doubts about a tile? Visit the tutorial screen and explore the different tile usages in the Tile Gallery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Levels</h2><br>Play hand-made levels and explore the Daily and Nightly challenge levels every new day. Each new daily level comes with different modifiers that will test your strategies. Discover new combinations of tiles to elevate your game to the next level!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/f48fb23e1dbc4356a848259ef80f7163.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/f48fb23e1dbc4356a848259ef80f7163.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/f48fb23e1dbc4356a848259ef80f7163.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buildings</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Factory<br></li><li>Central<br></li><li>Accelerator<br></li><li>Park<br></li><li>Overclocker<br></li><li>Investor<br></li><li>Jumper<br></li><li>Belt<br></li><li>Firecamp<br></li><li>Drums<br></li><li>Bishop<br></li><li>Casino<br></li><li>Water<br></li><li>Bitcoin<br></li><li>Portals<br></li><li>More...</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/ac071b7dc4e4b3228fa578ad5ae56474.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2><br>Coin Factory is a relaxing money-making game where you'll embark on a journey to wealth. Combine and level up factories, explore numerous synergies at your own pace, and unlock multiple tiers of buildings. Compete in daily challenge levels with exclusive bonus buildings, adding a special flavor to your experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/a924f6e62fc82ad505066420eda56683.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/a924f6e62fc82ad505066420eda56683.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/a924f6e62fc82ad505066420eda56683.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Community</h2><br>Join us on our Discord to share your strategies and highlights! Our team values your ideas and feedback; we aim for Coin Factory to provide a great relaxing experience for everybody.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Start by planning your strategy and placing your output tile. This tile will receive all the money you make and make it available for you to buy upgrades and new tiles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/cf10a6cb0918446e86ecacab454e9126.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/cf10a6cb0918446e86ecacab454e9126.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/cf10a6cb0918446e86ecacab454e9126.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From here, it's all about building up! Level up your factories and place better modifier factories to enhance your production. Discover the best matches and uncover secrets that will give you an advantage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/75ca8748795e0ee4476e6db9ee89861a.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/75ca8748795e0ee4476e6db9ee89861a.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/75ca8748795e0ee4476e6db9ee89861a.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have doubts about a tile? Visit the tutorial screen and explore the different tile usages in the Tile Gallery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Levels</h2><br>Play hand-made levels and explore the Daily and Nightly challenge levels every new day. Each new daily level comes with different modifiers that will test your strategies. Discover new combinations of tiles to elevate your game to the next level!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/f48fb23e1dbc4356a848259ef80f7163.poster.avif?t=1731273656\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/f48fb23e1dbc4356a848259ef80f7163.webm?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992500/extras/f48fb23e1dbc4356a848259ef80f7163.mp4?t=1731273656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buildings</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Factory<br></li><li>Central<br></li><li>Accelerator<br></li><li>Park<br></li><li>Overclocker<br></li><li>Investor<br></li><li>Jumper<br></li><li>Belt<br></li><li>Firecamp<br></li><li>Drums<br></li><li>Bishop<br></li><li>Casino<br></li><li>Water<br></li><li>Bitcoin<br></li><li>Portals<br></li><li>More...</li></ul>",
